    <!-- Metafields Structure Information -->
    <section class="metafields-info-section">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="h3">Metafields Structure for Vitals Product Tabs</h2>
          <p>The following metafields structure has been designed for the enhanced product tabs:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="metafields-grid">
            
            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.key_features</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Pipe-separated values (|)</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "Heavy-duty design|Built-in stops|400mm stroke|IP54 protection"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.technical_specs</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Key:Value pairs separated by pipes</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "Power: 230V AC|Stroke: 400mm|Max Leaf: 3.5m|Protection: IP54"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.applications</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Pipe-separated values (|)</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "Residential gates|Commercial access|Industrial entrances"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.benefits</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Pipe-separated values (|)</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "Enhanced security|Weather resistant|Reliable operation"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.installation</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Text description</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "Professional installation required|Concrete foundation needed"</p>
            </div>

            <div class="metafield-info">
              <h4>features.warranty</h4>
              <p><strong>Type:</strong> single_line_text_field</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> Text description</p>
              <p><strong>Example:</strong> "3-year motor warranty|1-year component warranty"</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Instructions Section -->
    <section class="instructions-section">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="h3">Implementation Instructions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="instructions-steps">
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h4>Import Enhanced CSV</h4>
                <p>Use the enhanced CSV file (<code>Product-list-Enhanced.csv</code>) to import products with improved descriptions and metafields data.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h4>Configure Metafields</h4>
                <p>Ensure the following metafields are created in your Shopify admin under Settings > Custom data:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Namespace: <code>features</code></li>
                  <li>Keys: <code>key_features</code>, <code>technical_specs</code>, <code>applications</code>, <code>benefits</code>, <code>installation</code>, <code>warranty</code></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h4>Add Product Tabs Block</h4>
                <p>In your product template, add the "Product Tabs (Vitals Enhanced)" block to display the tabbed interface with product information.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h4>Configure Vitals Integration</h4>
                <p>The product tabs will automatically integrate with Vitals app features and fire custom events for enhanced tracking and analytics.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .product-manager-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-background);
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-header {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.02);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
  }

  .card-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
  }

  .card-header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.7);
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .product-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .product-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-background);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(var(--color-link), 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
  }

  .product-card__header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
  }

  .product-card__title {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .product-card__sku {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.6);
    background: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.05);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .product-card__content h4 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgb(var(--color-link));
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .product-card__features,
  .product-card__specs {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .product-card__content ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .product-card__content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.8);
  }

  .product-card__price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(var(--color-link));
  }

  .compare-price {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.5);
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .metafields-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .metafield-info {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.08);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .metafield-info h4 {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: rgb(var(--color-link));
    background: rgba(var(--color-link), 0.05);
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .metafield-info p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.8);
  }

  .metafield-info code {
    background: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.1);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .instructions-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: rgb(var(--color-link));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.8);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .step-content ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.8);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .metafields-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .product-card__header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }
</style>